==English==
===Etymology===
From [[tri-]] + [[perfecta|(per)fecta]].

===Pronunciation===
{{IPA|/traɪˈfɛktə/}}

===Noun===
{{en-noun}}

# (''US, Australia, NZ'') A [[bet]] in which the [[winner|winners]] of the first three places ([[first]], [[second]], and [[third]]) are selected in the [[correct]] order
# (''US, Australia, NZ'') The [[situation]] of having three major [[accomplishment|accomplishments]] or [[achievement|achievements]] in a [[sport]], [[profession]], or [[pastime]]

